Company Overview of BrightFarms, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
BrightFarms, Inc. finances, designs, builds, and operates greenhouse farms at or near supermarkets and grocery retailers. Its farms produce fruits and vegetables, including baby leaf lettuces and herbs, salad greens, tomatoes, and basil. The company sells its products through retail stores in the United States. BrightFarms, Inc. was incorporated in 2010 and is based in New York, New York.


21 West 46th StreetSuite 1109New York, NY 10036United StatesFounded in 2010



